OL,3,CTwo former City traders' rate rigging
OL,4,Cconvictions overturned at Supreme Court
OL,6,FTwo former City traders, who were
OL,7,Fjailed for manipulating benchmark
OL,8,Finterest rates, have had their
OL,9,Fconvictions overturned at the Supreme
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FFormer Citigroup and UBS trader Tom
OL,13,FHayes was found guilty of multiple
OL,14,Fcounts of conspiracy to defraud over
OL,15,Fmanipulating the London Inter-Bank
OL,16,FOffered Rate (Libor) between 2006 and
OL,17,F2010.
