OL,3,CTwo former City traders' rate rigging
OL,4,Cconvictions overturned at Supreme Court
OL,6,FCarlo Palombo, ex-vice president of
OL,7,Feuro rates at Barclays bank, was found
OL,8,Fguilty of conspiring with others to
OL,9,Fsubmit false or misleading Euro
OL,10,FInterbank Offered Rate (Euribor)
OL,11,Fsubmissions between 2005 and 2009.
OL,13,FThe Court of Appeal dismissed appeals
OL,14,Ffrom both men in March last year. They
OL,15,Fthen took their cases to the Supreme
OL,16,FCourt.
