OL,4,Cconvictions overturned at Supreme Court
OL,6,FLord Leggatt continued: "When the
OL,7,Fflaws in the directions given at Mr
OL,8,FPalombo's trial are considered in
OL,9,Fcombination, it cannot safely be
OL,10,Fassumed that, without them, the jury
OL,11,Fwould still have been bound to convict
OL,12,FMr Palombo."Thus, his conviction also
OL,13,Fcannot stand."
OL,15,FHe added: "Accordingly, both appeals
OL,16,Fshould be allowed."
