OL,6,FThe Libor rate was previously used as
OL,7,Fa reference point around the world for
OL,8,Fsetting millions of pounds worth of
OL,9,Ffinancial deals, including car loans
OL,10,Fand mortgages.
OL,12,FIt was an interest rate average
OL,13,Fcalculated from figures submitted by a
OL,14,Fpanel of leading banks in London, with
OL,15,Feach one reporting what it would be
OL,16,Fcharged were it to borrow from other
OL,17,Finstitutions.
