OL,3,CTwo former City traders' rate rigging
OL,4,Cconvictions overturned at Supreme Court
OL,6,FEuribor was created along with the
OL,7,Feuro currency in 1999 as a benchmark
OL,8,Frate of interest for transactions in
OL,9,Feuros.In 2012, the Serious Fraud
OL,10,FOffice (SFO) began criminal
OL,11,Finvestigations into traders it
OL,12,Fsuspected of manipulating Libor and
OL,13,FEuribor.
OL,15,FMr Hayes was the first person to be
OL,16,Fprosecuted by the SFO, who opposed his
OL,17,Fand Mr Palombo's appeals at the
OL,18,FSupreme Court.
