OL,3,CTwo former City traders' rate rigging
OL,4,Cconvictions overturned at Supreme Court
OL,6,FThe SFO brought prosecutions against
OL,7,F20 individuals between 2013 and 2019,
OL,8,Fseven of whom were convicted at trial,
OL,9,Ftwo pleaded guilty and 11 were
OL,10,Facquitted.
OL,12,FMr Hayes had also been facing criminal
OL,13,Fcharges in the United States but these
OL,14,Fwere dismissed after two other men
OL,15,Finvolved in a similar case had their
OL,16,Fconvictions reversed in 2022.
OL,18,FMore to follow...
